RACE.RACE_TEXT: DELTA DOWNS RACE 1 5F Dirt CR: 79. Claiming Purse 14000. FOR FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON A RACE SINCE JULY 4, 2022 OR WHICH HAVE NOT WON TWO RACES IN 2022. Weight, 123 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since December 4 Allowed 3 lbs. Claiming Price $5,000.

LUKE'S CAJUN STAR settled in the middle of the pack then went four wide in upper stretch to make a late rally. JONATHAN WHO was off slow and passed tiring rival in the stretch. DAAHERS BULLY was hustled along to be off the pace in the two path and weakened. HOLDING FAST was void of speed and not a threat. KENSLEY'S HIPPIE was placed close up from three wide and gave way late.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: DELTA DOWNS RACE 2 7F Dirt CR: 74. Claiming Purse 14000. FOR FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON A RACE IN 2022. Weight, 123 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since December 4 Allowed 3 lbs. Claiming Price $5,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: DEALIN' STELEN was allowed to settle in the two path around the first turn then made a middle move, steadily gaining on the leaders to be up in the final strides. APPLEWOOD saved ground to the quarter pole then moved out to three wide to make a late run on the leaders, engaged the leader at the eighth pole to take the lead at the sixteenth pole but was nail at the wire. SUMMER APPEAL was allowed to settle around the first turn then made a rail bid down the backstretch and around the final turn, moved out to two wide in upper stretch and fought gamely in the stretch drive. CORVETTE SPIRIT pressed the pace from the three path around the first turn then took the lead at the half pole was headed at the eighth pole and gave way grudgingly. SOUTHPINE GIFT was always back. IRISH EXPECTATIONS went to the lead from the two path around the first turn to the half pole then vied for the lead to the quarter pole and weakened. OFF SIXES reared as the gates opened and was not a factor. STEWARDS INQUIRY INTO THE START OF THE RACE, AFTER A REVIEW STEWARDS DECLARED THAT OFF SIXES WAS THE CAUSE OF HIS OWN PROBLEMS AND WAS DECLARED A STARTER.
